headline: BIO-TECHNE TO PRESENT AT THE CITI 2024 GLOBAL HEALTHCARE CONFERENCE
summary: Bio-Techne Corporation (NASDAQ: TECH) today announced that Kim Kelderman, President and Chief Executive Officer, will present at the Citi 2024 Global Healthcare Conference on Wednesday, December 4, 2024, at 3:15 p.m. EST. A live webcast of the presentation can be accessed via the IR Calendar page of Bio-Techne's Investor Relations website at https://investors.bio-techne.com/ir-calendar.
